# /etc/desktop.icons — scene-file DE desktop launcher icons.
#
# Read by /bin/hamdesktop at startup (through its own namespace; no global
# bypass). One launcher per non-blank, non-'#' line:
#
#     label|type|action
#
#   label  : text drawn under the icon
#   type   : "folder" -> folder glyph; anything else -> document glyph
#   action : an absolute path. A /bin/* path is SPAWNed (its own window);
#            any other path is treated as a directory and opened in the
#            file manager.
#
# If this file is absent or empty, hamdesktop falls back to a built-in
# default set (Files / Terminal / Home).
Files|folder|/bin/hamfmscene
Terminal|file|/bin/hamtermscene
Calculator|file|/bin/hamcalcscene
Text Editor|file|/bin/hameditscene
Input Inspector|file|/bin/haminput
Install Hamnix|file|/bin/haminstallui
Control Center|file|/bin/hamctl
System Monitor|file|/bin/hammonscene
Calendar|file|/bin/hamcalscene
Notes|file|/bin/hamnotesscene
Log Viewer|file|/bin/hamlogscene
Home|folder|/
